# Installation

## CPAN
 1. Ensure the cpan client is in your path
    * `which cpan`
 1. cpan -i WebService::MyGengo
 1. Wait...

## By-hand
 1. `perl Makefile.PL`
    * When asked whether to install dependencies, select 'yes'
 1. `make && make test`
 1. `sudo make install`

## Live Sandbox Testing
 1. See the TESTING file.
